Capabilities

Microtips Technology is a leading technical manufacturers offering display modules, board assembly, audio equipments… serving global suppliers of Human-Machine-Interface technology. By combining design and engineering solutions with core electronics manufacturing and logistics services, vertically integrated with components technologies, we optimize our customers’ operations, lower their costs and reduce time to market 




