Microtips (Dongguan) Technology Inc. is a manufacturer and supplier of LCD modules and OEM productions. It produces a full range of color and monochrome character, graphic, and custom-made LCD modules. It also produces color STV, FSTN, COG, COB, TAB and integrated touch panels while OEM design and manufacturing are available on request.
Microtips (Dongguan) Technology Inc. is a manufacturer and supplier of LCD modules and OEM productions. It produces a full range of color and monochrome character, graphic, and custom-made LCD modules. It also produces color STV, FSTN, COG, COB, TAB and integrated touch panels while OEM design and manufacturing are available on request.Less





















