2016 Ultra Low Cost 4.3" TFT
Microtips is pleased to announce our new lowest cost 4.3" TFT module. This LCD display is available as a standard model with a 480x272px resolution (square pixels), 350nit (cd/m2) brightness, 500:1 contrast ratio, wide 140° viewing angle, standard -30 ~ 80°C temperature range, onboard...
 



Sunlight Readable Technology
