Microtips New Vivid Liquid Crystal Display (VLCD)
Microtips Technology is proud to introduce Vivid Liquid Crystal Display (VLCD); a re-engineered LCD. VLCD is a low cost alternative to the VFD. VLCD offers a higher brightness and an 800:1 contrast, wide viewing angles and wide temperature ranges of OT=-30c to +80c and ST= -40c to +80c; with an added heater, VLCD’s have up to 40c OT. The non-sticking surface eliminates burn-in image issues associated with VFD. There is no need for color filters on a VLCD...
   



