Color TFT LCDs
Microtips Technology brings to you a whole new range of products from the latest in LCD technology. A TFT LCD or color LCD module is a variant of an LCD which uses thin film transistor technology to improve an image quality.  Color LCD module is use in many appliances such as television, computer monitors, kindles, mobile phone, and navigation system within a airplane cockpit and much more.We have a rich inventory of products manufactured at our facilities  in Taiwan and Mainland China.

   



 






Mono Graphic LCDs
Choose from any of our Graphic LCD or Monochrome LCD displays to enjoy crystal clear viewing in all areas of application. We offer a wide range of LCD displays for automotive interiors, medical appliances, and hi-bright wide view LCDs for outdoors, and indoor use in various consumer and industrial areas.  Our displays perform a brilliant job on all kinds of text, graphics, pictures and full motion video. Most of our displays are available
   



 






Character LCDs
Character Liquid crystal displays come in many sizes which is often name by the number of rows and columns. Microtips Technology produces a whole range of Character LCD modules that are used in a wide variety of application areas from fax machines, and laser printers, to different industrial test equipments, and networking equipments such as, routers and storage devices. The Character LCD screens as the name implied, can display only text.
   



 


 



